# Phase 01: CampusHat Backend — Project Setup & Configuration

Build the complete Django 4.2 production-grade backend foundation inside `backend/` directory on the `backend` branch. This creates the project skeleton, Docker infrastructure, core mixins, and DRF configuration for the CampusHat e-commerce/marketplace platform.

## Proposed Changes

### .gitignore Update

#### [MODIFY] [.gitignore](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/.gitignore)
- Add Python/Django-specific ignore patterns (`.pyc`, `__pycache__`, `*.egg-info`, `db.sqlite3`, `venv/`, `staticfiles/`, `mediafiles/`)

