### Requirements

#### [NEW] [base.txt](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/requirements/base.txt)
All core dependencies pinned: Django 4.2, DRF 3.15, psycopg2-binary, redis, celery, django-filter, django-cors-headers, djangorestframework-simplejwt, django-storages, boto3, Pillow, python-decouple, drf-spectacular, gunicorn

