### Django Config (`backend/config/`)

#### [NEW] [base.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/config/settings/base.py)
Modular base settings with `python-decouple`. PostgreSQL, Redis cache, Celery, REST_FRAMEWORK (JWT auth, custom pagination, custom exception handler), SIMPLE_JWT, CORS, S3 block, email block, drf-spectacular. `AUTH_USER_MODEL = 'authentication.User'`.

#### [NEW] [development.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/config/settings/development.py)
DEBUG=True, ALLOWED_HOSTS=['*'], debug-toolbar, local file storage.

#### [NEW] [production.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/config/settings/production.py)
DEBUG=False, ALLOWED_HOSTS from env, SSL/HSTS, S3 storage, Sentry init.

#### [NEW] [celery.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/config/celery.py)
Standard Celery app for Django with autodiscover, beat schedule placeholder.

#### [NEW] [urls.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/config/urls.py)
Project-level URLs: admin, api/v1/ namespace, spectacular schema/docs.

#### [NEW] [wsgi.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/config/wsgi.py) / [asgi.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/config/asgi.py) / [__init__.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/config/__init__.py)

