#### [NEW] [models.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/core/models.py)
UUIDMixin, TimestampMixin, SoftDeleteMixin (with SoftDeleteManager), BaseModel (combines all three, abstract).

#### [NEW] [permissions.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/core/permissions.py)
IsVerifiedStudent, IsApprovedSeller, IsAdminOrModerator, IsOwnerOrAdmin, ReadOnly.

#### [NEW] [pagination.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/core/pagination.py)
CampusHatPagination (page_size=20, max=100), CampusHatCursorPagination (feed-style).

#### [NEW] [exceptions.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/core/exceptions.py)
CampusHatException base class, custom_exception_handler wrapping DRF default.

#### [NEW] [renderers.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/core/renderers.py)
CampusHatJSONRenderer — consistent `{success, data/errors, message}` envelope.

#### [NEW] [utils.py](file:///c:/Parsonal%20Website/CampusHat/backend/core/utils.py)
generate_order_number, generate_invoice_number, generate_tracking_code, generate_store_system_id, get_file_upload_path, send_notification_email.

